{"tid":381312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求巴絲打氣","createTime":"2017-08-30T22:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T10:49:22.000Z","uid":136572,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"031a852a219728b8226db6b7e86f27c144bf0f10","tid":381312,"uid":136572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T22:15:07.000Z","msg":"等陣我最親最愛嘅長輩就要做手術<br />\n雖然風險好細 但佢年紀唔細同埋啲醫生又講到鬼咁多特別情況<br />\n搞到我依加好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好錫所有孫 我都好尊敬佢<br />\n我自問2017年都未有啲咩運仔<br />\n我祈求今次可以將我今年未用嘅所有運仔比晒佢去免除埋果幾%嘅風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要順利過關呀 公公 加油<br />\n希望巴絲幫小弟集氣等佢一切順順利利 身體健康"},{"pid":"99738e651501bc8e4ec28dd932e38ce7318fb466","tid":381312,"uid":45831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:05:23.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6e5cc340f882ee562786e55c24a6fee5f7ea3a","tid":381312,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:07:21.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7c86f13865f693549e80768f50ee2864d04003","tid":381312,"uid":110098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafd6a60156380262737269752b0f4e5294c24a1","tid":381312,"uid":136572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750a8bb96feb13240714d6e594a8ad954c285c7c","tid":381312,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"加油！一切順利！祝樓主全家健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccd5e179f3c2d5e988f02497444837622a02b3b","tid":381312,"uid":2